		;  * USB Descriptor - placed in CONSTHIGH segment.
		;  * Generated from DDDUsbDescriptor.ucf (1 MIDI IN & 1 MIDI OUT, no Audio).
		;  * Kept as-is; stored in ROM/const segment so does NOT contribute to CODEHIGH.
		;  */
